  "description": "<p><u><strong>Seeking for Production Technician / Mechanical Engineer</strong></u></p><p><strong>Location</strong>: Tuas Crescent MRT </p><p><strong>Working hours</strong>: 6 days a week</p><p><strong>Salary</strong>: $3000-$5000<br /><br /><strong>Job scope</strong><br />1) Manage extrusion moulding, blow moulding, injection moulding machines<br />2) Maintainence work on air compressors, chillers, dryers, cooling towers<br />3) Packing bottles and caps<br />4) Assisting with crushing of recycled plastic material<br />5) Follow production plan<br /><br /><strong>Requirements</strong><br />Diploma or bachelor in mechanical engineering<br />At least 2-3 years of experience in manufacturing line and dealing with machinery</p><p><u><strong>Benefits</strong></u><br />Yearly salary increment<br />Yearly performance bonus<br />Career progression<br />Friendly and teaching culture<br /></p><p>If keen to whatsapp text Eileen +65 8887 0896<br />https://wa.me/6588870896</p>",
