    "description": "<p>SUPERPET PLASTIC PTE LTD</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Superpet Plastic Pte Ltd</strong> is a leading manufacture in plastic bottles, caps and preforms which was established in the year 1986. Superpet Plastic shifted from Kim Chuan Terrace to the existing location in the year of May 1999.&nbsp; This newly built factory has a built in area of 12,300 square meters. This expansion increases our production capacity and capability and enables us to further penetrate into local, as well as the foreign market.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We pride ourselves on our ability to provide quality services and products to our valuable customers through ONE STOP SERVICE.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>To provide excellent and consistent services and products to our valued customers, we constantly</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Make high investment in the sophisticated and latest available technologies;</li>\n  <li>Training and upgrading of the skills and knowledge of our dedicated staff;</li>\n  <li>Searching a world class quality system.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Superpet Plastic is one of the pioneer companies in the industry who has attained ISO 9001, an international recognized quality system.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At present, Superpet Plastic has set up 2 production plants in Tianjin &amp; Zhangjiagang of China to manufacture and supply quality bottles and caps to MNCs companies such as Shell, ESSO, and some well established China companies.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>With our excellent customers support and dedicated staff, Superpet’s globalisation ambitions will soon be realised.</p>",
